title: Postgame Show: Being Alarmed By Your Alarm
description:
Russell Wilson is a candidate for the new "JJ Watt, doin' too much" role in the NFL. Jessica is waking up with extreme anxiety due to the sound of her alarm. And what is the proper etiquette for discarding items you’ve tried on in a fitting room that you’re not going to buy?
